Dependencies:

* A reasonable modern C++ compiler
* SDL
* SDL_image
* SDL_ttf
* SDL_mixer
* SDL_net
* GLEW
* libcurl
* LibLUA 5.0 or later

Compilation on UNIX systems:

./configure
make

It is then run by running src/rts. The game attempts to locate its files
through rules in src/paths.cpp, and it obeys both XDG_DATA_DIRS and
XDG_CONFIG_DIRS.

Currently installation does not work, so do not attempt a make install.
